<html>
<head>
<style type="text/css">
.vm-container {
	margin: 10px;
}
.vm-page-content {
	border: 1px solid #2a3f54;
	height: 100%;
	color: #000;
}

.vm-page-content .head {
	background-color: #2a3f54;
	padding: 10px;
	color: #FFFFFF;
}

.head .images {
	margin-left: 10px;
}

.vm-page-content .body {
	padding: 10px;
	font-size: 12px;
}
.resp{
margin: 5px 0px;
}
.resp h5 {
	font-size: 13px;
	font-weight: 600;
}

.body .cont p {
	margin: 0 0 8px;
	text-align: justify;
	line-height: 20px;
}

.sub-title {
	font-size: 13px;
	font-weight: 600;
	line-height: 30px;
}

.sub-mrg-content {
	margin-top: 3px;
	margin-bottom: 3px;
	padding-left: 30px;
}
.sub-mrg-content li{
line-height: 25px;
}
.btn{
padding: 10px;
background:  #2a3f54;
color: #ffffff;
margin: 5px;
text-align: center;
border-radius:3px;
}
.footer {
	padding: 10px;
	background: #fff;
}
.footer-reg{
font-size: 12px;
	color: #000;
	font-weight: 600;
	line-height: 20px;
}
.footer .quas {
	margin-top: 20px;
	font-size: 12px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="vm-container">
	<div class="vm-page-content">
		<div class="head">
			<div class="images">
				<img src="cid:imagess"alt="MyJobKart"/>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="body">
			<div class="resp">
				<h5>Dear Sir/Medam,</h5>
			</div>
			<div class="cont">
				<p>Your payment has been approved and your product has been successfully updated.</p>
				<p>You have enrolled <b>${pType}</b> product. We can provide a service for this product as</p>
					<ul class="sub-mrg-content">
					<li>you can download 10000 resumes before the expired date.</li>
					<li>You can post 100+ job openings.</li>
					<li>You can create 10 sub-users.</li>
				</ul>
				<div class="sub-title">Product Details:</div>
				<ul class="sub-mrg-content">
					<li><b>Product Type :</b> ${pType}</li>
					<li><b>Total Amount :</b> ${pAmount}</li>
					<li><b>Validity Month :</b> ${Pmonth}</li>
					<li><b>Transaction Date :</b> ${pDate}</li>
					<li><b>Transaction No :</b> ${pNo}</li>
					<li><b>Transaction Status :</b> ${pStatus}</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer">
			<div class="footer-reg">
				Best Regards<br /> MyJobKart.com
			</div>
			<div class="quas">
				Have a question? E-mail at <b>info.myjobkart@gmail.com</b>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</body></html>
